name: Moonlight Bakery
description:
Moonlight Bakery 

21 years old Natalia, she loves to baked, more specifically she love to baked soft chewie cookies, her special Choco Chip Marshmallow Cookies are the most favorable among the other recipes at her bakery store. 

She love doing some experiments and this often leave her a big mess inside the kitchen. Sometimes she add jasmine tea brew, watermelon juice, she even add casava chips or even tempe, she never new they tasted good as cookies. She tried dozens of recipes until she found the best formula for her unique recepies, most importantly she have so much fun doing it. 

00:34 seconds, 1080x1080p.

short story + music + illustration + animation by Sartje
